38 //
39 // Cylindrical bound for quadrotor controls. Circle in (pitch, roll), and
40 // intervals in yaw_rate and thrust.
41 //
43 
44 #ifndef FASTRACK_CONTROL_QUADROTOR_CONTROL_BOUND_CYLINDER_H
45 #define FASTRACK_CONTROL_QUADROTOR_CONTROL_BOUND_CYLINDER_H
46 
47 #include <fastrack/control/control_bound.h>
48 #include <fastrack/control/quadrotor_control.h>
49 #include <fastrack/control/scalar_bound_interval.h>
50 
51 #include <math.h>
52 
53 namespace fastrack {
54 namespace control {
55 
56 class QuadrotorControlBoundCylinder : public ControlBound<QuadrotorControl> {
57 public:
58  ~QuadrotorControlBoundCylinder() {}
59  explicit QuadrotorControlBoundCylinder(double radius,
60  double ScalarBoundInterval &yaw_rate,
61  double ScalarBoundInterval &thrust)
62  : pitch_roll_radius_(radius), yaw_rate_interval_(yaw_rate),
63  thrust_interval_(thrust) {}
64 
65  // Derived classes must be able to check whether a query is inside the
66  // bound.
67  inline bool Contains(const QuadrotorControl &query) const {
68  return std::hypot(query.pitch, query.roll) < pitch_roll_radius_ &&
69  yaw_rate_interval_.Contains(query.yaw_rate) &&
70  thrust_interval_.Contains(query.thrust);
71  }
72 
73  // Derived classes must be able to compute the projection of a vector
74  // (represented as the templated type) onto the surface of the bound.
75  // NOTE: We will treat this vector as emanating from the natural origin
76  // of the bound so that it constitutes a meaningful direction with respect
77  // to that origin.
78  inline QuadrotorControl
79  ProjectToSurface(const QuadrotorControl &query) const {
80  // Compute scaling to project (pitch, roll) onto the cylinder.
81  const double scaling =
82  pitch_roll_radius_ / std::hypot(query.pitch, query.roll);
83 
84  return QuadrotorControl(scaling * query.pitch, scaling * query.roll,
85  yaw_rate_interval_.ProjectToSurface(query.yaw_rate),
86  thrust_interval_.ProjectToSurface(query.thrust));
87  }
88 
89 private:
90  // Radius in (pitch, roll) dimensions.
91  const double pitch_roll_radius_;
92 
93  // Intervals in yaw_rate and thrust.
94  const ScalarBoundInterval yaw_rate_interval_;
95  const ScalarBoundInterval thrust_interval_;
96 }; //\class ControlBound
97 
98 } // namespace control
99 } // namespace fastrack
